NXC can be found here:

Windows:
    http://bricxcc.sourceforge.net/test_release.zip
    
    Place the nbc.exe in the win32 folder
    
Mac:
    http://bricxcc.sourceforge.net/nbc/beta/nbc-1.0.1.b36.osx.tgz
    
    Place nbc and nxtcom in the darwin folder
    
Linux:
    http://bricxcc.sourceforge.net/nbc/beta/nbc-1.0.1.b36.tgz

    Haven't implemented for linux.  Take the nbc, and put it in a folder
    with the name obtained by:
    
    import sys
    print sys.platform
    
    